  "mangledDe": {
    "_comment": [
      "de-DE ONLY. ASCII-mangled German: umlaut/eszett digraphs that were never restored,",
      "inherited from the mangled German dictionary in .orchestration/logs/e16-translate.mjs",
      "(t2). That script is NOT part of the build and must NOT be revived or 'fixed' — the",
      "DATA it produced is what needs repair, in de-DE.json.",
      "es-ES / fr-FR / it-IT / pt-PT were probed and are clean; this class is de-only.",
      "",
      "Stems, matched case-insensitively as whole-ish words. Deliberately stem-based rather",
      "than a blanket /ae|oe|ue|ss/ rule, because plenty of correct German carries those",
      "digraphs legitimately (\"Passwort\", \"Adresse\", \"Aktuell\") — a blanket rule would bury",
      "the real hits in noise."
    ],
